high_descs: walk out of the bedroom and go into the diningtable.
pick up the butterknife from the table that has the microwave on it.
turn around and walk to the bread room.
use the knife to cut the potato on top of the bread.
Turn around and face the desk on both sides then put the knife away.
turn around and look at the butterknife on the desk.
pick up a piece of potato of the desk.
Take the bread and walk back into the living room.
go to the fridge.
Put the bread in the storage and then remove it from the storage.
walk over to the microwave.
Put the bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Get a slice of bread and bring it to the living room to put in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, exit the diningtable, go right and then turn left and go to the microwave.
Pick up the butterknife from the table.
Turn left and go back into the bedroom on the left and go to the bread.
Slice the bread on the table.
Turn right and then turn left to face the desk.
Place the butterknife on the desk.
Turn right to face the desk.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn right, exit the room, turn right and then turn left and go to the fridge.
Place the slice of bread in the bottom of the fridge, close the door and the pick the bread back up.
Move right to the microwave.
Place the bread in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of Bread in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to the end of the path, turn right and enter the big room, walk to the sofa on the right and then left until you are about to pass a diningtable to your left.
Pick up a butterknife from next to the microwave.
Go back to the room you came from and move to the opposite corner, in front of the bread table.
Cut the bread on the table with the knife.
Take a small step towards the desk.
Drop the butterknife on the desk.
Move back to the left of the desk.
Pick up a bread slice from the table.
Go back to where you saw the microwave, but take a further step to the right so that you are in front of the fridge.
Put the bread slice in the fridge, let the bread cool there for a while, then take the bread out.
Take a step left to be positioned in front of the microwave.
Put the bread slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled bread in the microwave.
